name: Ordinals ALPHA.bet
description: Ordinals ALPHA.bet is the first Alphabet collection A-Z on the Ordinal protocol. Each Ordinal represents a different letter of the Alphabet in an unique style. The lower the letter, the higher the rarity i.e. A is the rarest and Z is the least rare but since there are only 26 Ordinals in this collection and it's the first Alphabet Ordinal collection, every Ordinal is extremely rare.
